    <div xml:id="PN317">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>veṉvēl<gap quantity="34" reason="lost" unit="character"/>natu</l>
<l>muṉṟiṟ kiṭanta peruṅkaḷi yāḷaṟ</l>
<l>kataḷuṇ ṭāyiṉum pāyuṇṭāyiṉum</l>
<l>yātuṇ ṭāyiṉuṅ koṭumiṉ vallē</l>
<l>vēṭkai mīḷapa <gap quantity="7" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap quantity="14" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ku memakkum piṟarkkum</l>
<l>yārkku mīyntu tuyilēṟ piṉaṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>To the highly intoxicated man who lies in the front yard</l>
<l>give, be it a skin, be it a mat,</l>
<l>be it whatever, quickly!</l>
<l/>
<l>He got sleep [only] after having given to us, </l>
<l>to others, to everyone.</l>
</lg>
